    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "nrVeE3oDH0tNFm9CX5stkYPKAaCrnePTkJZtrLHmoDg=",
    "originContent": "## Features",
    "translatedContent": "## 特性  "
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "XvXNIzuQ1kBN51TRnWdY0JYyfn3nmeOEawyzSuOWaTA=",
    "originContent": "- **Block-level CPU/GPU swapping** — only 8 of 40 transformer layers on GPU at once (~6GB vs ~30GB)",
    "translatedContent": "- **块级 CPU/GPU 交换** — GPU 上同时仅运行40层变换器中的8层（约6GB 对比约30GB）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "hBzoerLvDg6M3eDtAWkhl1dWiQ7s6fAUOR/irhT9uwo=",
    "originContent": "- **Async CUDA prefetching** — next block transfers while current block computes",
    "translatedContent": "- **异步 CUDA 预取** — 当前块计算时预传输下一个块  "
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "5HBZQiRgTkkpZp5zDurtdRAA66Waohz8cLaUdYwyjg4=",
    "originContent": "- **Distill mode** — 8-step generation without CFG (fastest)",
    "translatedContent": "- **蒸馏模式** — 8步生成无 CFG（最快）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "TdUgf9qNNG7thz8l4iXrMDwgN+o7AQkOi2KFUiB0Vz4=",
    "originContent": "- **1080p super-resolution** — latent-space upscaling from 256p base",
    "translatedContent": "- **1080p 超分辨率** — 从256p基础潜变量空间上采样  "
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "6bUQ1t2iny8lfM1UrNtXqOQJiMUoa0BSt+ZIv5ijxLs=",
    "originContent": "- **TurboVAE decoder** — sliding window decode with output offload for 1080p",
    "translatedContent": "- **TurboVAE 解码器** — 滑动窗口解码并输出卸载支持1080p  "
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "Gc8sCnylCVEYH5ZRAdRyk4wqIqE+PPksKbnO0DtVMZM=",
    "originContent": "- **Audio + video** — single-stream joint generation",
    "translatedContent": "- **音频 + 视频** — 单流联合生成  "
  },
